  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to investigate the effect of addition of different doses of Ketamine
      locally in acute and chronic post-mastectomy pain after breast cancer surgery and on the
      probability of developing chronic post-mastectomy pain.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
